title: 'Poor engineering of product'
body: Packing was gud. One of the metallic bracket is shaking becoz the rivet is bigger than the bracket dimension. Thus bracket is uneven and cannot be secured to the wall evenly. One side of bracket has more bending angle that the screws cannot be fixed evenly. No hole in one of the bracket to fix the screw to wall. Poor quality screws. Just tightened them on POP wall and screws bent. Had to call a carpenter, who'll charge Rs1000 Rs to punch a hole in the bracket to drive the screw to fix on wall, supply sturdy screws, and straighten the uneven brackets by changing the rivet. Poor engineering. Seller should take care to do the measurement properly prior to dispatch to avoid unwanted inconvenience for buyer. Have to return the product and seek refund as additional burden of 1000 Rs is not acceptable.

title: 'Space-Saving Elegance: Qara Solid Wall-Mounted Table Review'
body: Qara Solid Wall-Mounted Table is an outstanding addition to any living space. Its superb quality, effortless installation, and space-saving design make it a standout piece of furniture. While a broader range of design options would be a welcome addition, this minor consideration pales in comparison to the overall excellence of the product. If you're in search of a versatile, durable, and elegant space-saving solution, the Qara table is a superb choice that won't disappoint.
